import React from 'react'
import {  Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Navbar  from './Navbar'
import ProductPage from './ProductPage'


function Main() {


  return (
    <>
    <Routes>
    <Route path='/navbar' element={<Navbar />} />
    <Route path='/' element={<ProductPage  />} />
    </Routes>
    </>
  )
}

export default Main
